headline: Work Underway to Strengthen Electric Grid in York County
summary: FirstEnergy Pennsylvania Electric Company (FE PA), a FirstEnergy Corp. (NYSE: FE) subsidiary doing business as Met-Ed in eastern Pennsylvania, is completing work to upgrade its energy delivery system in northwestern York County to help prevent or minimize the length of service disruptions, particularly during cold or hot weather when customers use more electricity to stay comfortable.
